    <h1>How to Play</h1>
    <p>Welcome to the battlefield, commander! Here's everything you need to know to dominate in Tank Game:</p>
    
    <h2>Objective</h2>
    <p>Destroy enemy tanks while protecting yourself and your base.<br>
    Survive as long as possible to rack up points and climb the leaderboard!</p>
    
    <h2>Controls</h2>
    <p>Arrow Keys: Move your tank in different directions.<br>
    Up: Move forward.<br>
    Down: Move backward.<br>
    Left/Right: Rotate your tank.<br>
    Spacebar: Fire your cannon to destroy enemies.<br>
    Enter: Pause the game or access the menu.</p>
    
    <h2>Scoring System</h2>
    <p>+10 Points for destroying an enemy tank.<br>
    +5 Points for avoiding enemy fire.<br>
    -5 Points for getting hit.</p>
